{"url":"https://www.meisei-kogyo.co.jp/ir/management/message/","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n\r\n<head>\r\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\r\n  <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=Edge\">\r\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n  <meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\r\n\r\n  <title>株主の皆さまへ｜経営情報｜IR情報｜明星工業株式会社</title>\r\n  <meta name=\"description\" content=\"大阪府大阪市。化学プラントなどの熱絶縁工事業。会社組織・IR情報、工事実績と製品案内。\">\r\n  <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"断熱,断熱材,熱絶縁,化学プラント,保温,保冷,LNG,LPG,液化天然ガス,耐火被覆,築炉,環境エネルギー,焼却炉,煙突ライニング,防音,アスベスト対策,スターベローズ,非金属製伸縮継手\">\r\n  <link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://www.meisei-kogyo.co.jp/corporate/\">\r\n  <link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/icon/favicon.ico\">\r\n\r\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Noto+Serif+JP:400,500,600,700,900&display=swap&subset=japanese\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\r\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/css/all.css\">\r\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/css/reset.css\">\r\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/css/common.css\">\r\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/css/style.css\">\r\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/css/ir/ir.css\">\r\n\r\n  <script src=\"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.min.js\"></script>\r\n  <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js\"></script>\r\n  <script src=\"https://www.promisejs.org/polyfills/promise-6.1.0.min.js\"></script>\r\n  <script src=\"/js/common.js\"></script>\r\n  <script src=\"/js/corporate.js\"></script>\r\n</head>\r\n\r\n<body>\r\n  <div id=\"wrapper\">\r\n\r\n    \n<header class=\"header\">\n  <h1 class=\"header_logo\">\n    <a href=\"/\"><img src=\"/img/common/logo.png\"></a>\n  </h1>\n    <div class=\"Toggle\" id=\"js_sideMenuBtn\">\n      <span></span><span></span><span></span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"NavMenu\">\n    <div class=\"menu\">\n      <div class=\"nav\">\n        <div class=\"langua